{"id": 1417, "genre": 1001, "title": "那些老家伙说豆瓣猫眼恶评是对电影产业的伤害，你怎么看？", "description": "哎呀，吃了屎还不许人说屎难吃，真霸道。（题图来自：Yukai Du）", "record_count": 5560, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161229102008qjp64cXydt2SWFZ8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-12-29T03:00:40Z", "options": [{"id": 148992, "content": "有一句两句可能是故意为之，都是差评，那是真恶心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794545}, {"id": 149248, "content": "真扯淡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 822201}, {"id": 150785, "content": "还是别看了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184261}, {"id": 148994, "content": "呵呵，好电影你用宣传？你们有本事把烂片吹成世纪典藏。也是世纪典藏烂片", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879955}, {"id": 148739, "content": "票房差不从自身找原因还怪别人也是没谁了。今年品质高的电影可能是因为宣传力度不够，档期短和排片少等因素的影响，导致票房不理想。但品质低的电影照样票房不理想这是为什么呢？占着茅坑不拉?呗！还有别把我们当傻子，品质糟糕的电影票房怎会高！我们是对电影越来越挑剔，不是怕花那点钱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702581}, {"id": 148740, "content": "仁者见仁智者见智，大众的口味又不是导演说了算", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 421057}, {"id": 148996, "content": "开门，查水表", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852809}, {"id": 149764, "content": "好奇心已经说了\n\n他们是老家伙，等他们死了就对了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692837}, {"id": 148741, "content": "这些老家伙的言行体现了极其弱智的懵逼行为。吃皇家狗粮吃多了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155527}, {"id": 148997, "content": "可能只是伤害了他们疯狂敛财?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780866}, {"id": 148742, "content": "别在影院上映，别拍，不就没人说难看了，真是蠢的吓人?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880903}, {"id": 148998, "content": "恶心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844361}, {"id": 149510, "content": "看过就不说了，没看过瞎跟风。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864133}, {"id": 148743, "content": "给好评乃至捧上天的时候为何闭眼享受不说话？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 828920}, {"id": 148999, "content": "我正是抱着看这片有多烂的这种态度才去看的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851220}, {"id": 153095, "content": "我发现我对某局真的非常无话可说……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902601}, {"id": 150792, "content": "讓他們說去吧，他們以為有人信就好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 750777}, {"id": 149001, "content": "跟不上大众的眼光，只能活在自己曾经的辉煌里！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883547}, {"id": 148746, "content": "那些一味地无脑给好评的，是不是也要禁止评论啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880903}, {"id": 149002, "content": "就这么个神奇的国度，你还表达什么言论自由。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112082}, {"id": 151306, "content": "吹出来的口碑 造出来的票房 很快就会原形毕露 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893763}, {"id": 148747, "content": "都不看就消停了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666852}, {"id": 149003, "content": "一向不看国产片", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807391}, {"id": 148749, "content": "有不少人喜欢的就打5星，不喜欢的就打1星，没有中间分数，所以并不是完全的客观", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 850707}, {"id": 149005, "content": "恶心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814333}, {"id": 149773, "content": "对，就是恶评", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 887222}, {"id": 148750, "content": "广电焦虑了>:)\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 866572}, {"id": 149262, "content": "我们也得有自己的价值观才行，不能老靠老一辈人给我们灌输", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 885141}, {"id": 150798, "content": "在一个后真相时代，评论还有那么重要吗？大家只是表达一种情绪而已。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 888314}, {"id": 148751, "content": "烂就是烂，还不让说了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883083}, {"id": 148752, "content": "说破天去我也不买票", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770545}, {"id": 148753, "content": "不许百姓点灯…", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883945}, {"id": 149009, "content": "言论无自由可谈了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880173}, {"id": 150545, "content": "中国人没有说话权了，才是真的可怕！\n那位说“豆瓣等是有义务，治理恶意差评或好评现象”的人，我很赞成。绝对不能因为有了真正的喷子，捧子，而否定了所有人的说话的权利！绝对不能！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889355}, {"id": 151569, "content": "不让恶评那我们不看了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349453}, {"id": 148754, "content": "我花钱买你的票看了一部催眠的辣鸡电影，还不准我看完之后哔哔几句了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789686}, {"id": 149010, "content": "精品自然分高，豆瓣猫眼还没有高分片了？  拍的好看的人自然认可", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880173}, {"id": 151826, "content": "国内电影要走向全球，当然在观众心里会和其他国家电影（主要和好莱坞大片）相比，好莱坞这么发达的影视产业产出的不少大制作电影都会被观众认为是烂片（评分低），所以宣传屌屌的实际看起来不如预期而被打低分很正常。干嘛打多少分都要管，这才是对电影行业的危害", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 845252}, {"id": 148755, "content": "国产片需要保护，但是你得有水平啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833064}, {"id": 149012, "content": "汽车人总动员绝对没有抄袭\n迪士尼肯定给了法院的压力\n观众肯定受了大v号的影响\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 884583}, {"id": 148501, "content": "用点名批评豆瓣和猫眼的办法来压制观影人群正常的发声渠道，无耻", "image": null, "praise_count": 350, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 149013, "content": "解决问题，解决有问题的嘴即可", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133780}, {"id": 148758, "content": "一切从实际出发啊，党校学的东西都忘了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770545}, {"id": 149014, "content": "我誓死捍卫我说话的权利", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760698}, {"id": 149015, "content": "问题来了，甜甜后台是谁？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 877473}, {"id": 148504, "content": "“头疼缝嘴”", "image": null, "praise_count": 990, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 148760, "content": "醉了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 881021}, {"id": 149016, "content": "治大国若烹小鲜，然而次次都扔只孙大圣进去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216033}, {"id": 149784, "content": "亲戚聚会", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869083}, {"id": 148505, "content": "并不想当烂片的守护小天使，谢谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 234, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}]}